Class GenericDiffBean.ColorDiffRevisionVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.cam.caret.sakai.rwiki.tool.bean.GenericDiffBean.ColorDiffRevisionVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RevisionVisitor
    Enclosing class:
    GenericDiffBean

    public class GenericDiffBean.ColorDiffRevisionVisitor
extends Object
implements RevisionVisitor
    RevisionVisitor that will generate a listed diff view Notes:
    • Each line is given it's own div.
    • A deleted line has the class deleted.
    • An added line has the class added.
    • An unchanged line has the class unchanged.
    • A changed line is display as an div with class original followed by a div with class changed

    andrew
